  "text": "In addition to their plant growth promoting effects, Rhizobium spp. have been increasingly associated with disease suppressive effects in the recent literature [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . Improvements in plant health are mediated by two different ecological mechanisms: (1) antagonism of pest and pathogens and (2) stimulation of plant host defenses.",
